! Title: Cybo's Android Element Hiding
! Description: A compliment to the basic hosts file that will hide annoying elements or ad placeholders for Android devices with AdGuard.
! Expires: 8 hours
! Version: 1
! Last Modified: Monday, October 26, 2020

! This is in a separate list as AdGuard on
! Android doesn't support generic rules
! like what I use in the main hosts file
! and cosmstic filtering overall can
! significantly impact page loading times
! on slower devices

